title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 326-1.3 - Investigation of application
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 326-1.3 - Investigation of application

State Regulations

The county medical society or the workers' compensation
committee of the county medical society, as the case may be, shall investigate
and pass upon the application within 60 days of such filing. Notes

326-1.3
